constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the given beacon address and optional initialization data.

fallback.description: A fallback function that is called when no other function matches. Can receive Ether.

receive.description: A receive function that is called when the contract receives Ether without any data.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the contract's admin changes.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the contract's implementation is upgraded.
